The article is a press gaggle by Principal Deputy Press Secretary Eric Schultz, conducted aboard Air Force One en route to Las Vegas, Nevada. Schultz discusses various topics including immigration reform, the President's executive actions, the economic benefits of these actions, the reaction from Speaker Boehner and House Republicans, and the timeline for implementation. Schultz also mentions the President's upcoming trip to India and provides a week ahead schedule of the President's activities. The article concludes with a brief mention of the ongoing negotiations with Iran regarding their nuclear program.